  <brief_title>Evaluation of Behavioral Health-Virtual Patient Navigation Team (BH-VPN)</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Evaluation of ED to Admission Conversion Among Patients With a Telepsychiatric Consult Who Are Followed by a Behavioral Health - Virtual Patient Navigation Team</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Carolinas Healthcare System</agency>
